						some or all of the attorney fees of the person making a claim against
						you must be paid by you. The amount that must be paid by you is
						determined by Alaska Rule of Civil Procedure 82. We provide coverage
						for attorney fees for which you are liable under Alaska Rule of Civil
						Procedure 82 subject to the following limitation:
					</fo:block>
					
